text: Hugh Marjoribanks (born 12 August 1933) is an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales in 1958/59. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:People from Mackay, Queensland
